==Lilongwe==

* [http://weather.msn.com/local.aspx?&wealocations=wc%3aMIXX0002&q=Lilongwe%2c+MWI&setunit=C nyengo mu Mzinda wa [[Lilongwe]] ku choka ku MSN]
'''Lilongwe''', ndi mzinda omwe umazeka m'diko la [[Malawi]]ndipo uli ndi anthu Pafupi fupi 1,600,000 ndipo ndi kapitolo ya dziko la [[Malawi]]. Mzinda wa [[Lilongwe]] umapezeka m'dera la pkati m'diko la [[Malawi]],ndipo udakhala pa Mstinge wawuku wa [[Lilongwe]],pafupi ndi malile a [[Malawi]] ndi [[Mozambique]] ndi [[Zambia]]. Mseu wawukulu wa M1 umadutsa pakatikati pa mzindau,ndipo msueu uwu ndi wawukulu m'diko lonse la [[Malawi] ]. Mzinda wa [[Lilongwe]] umapezeka pa {{coord|13|59|S|33|47|E}} (-13.98333, 33.78333). [http://earth-info.nga.mil/gns/html/cntry_files.html]

==Mbiri==
Mzindawu udayamba moyo wake ngati mudzi wayun'gono chabe mphepete mwa mstinge wawukulu wa Lilongwe,pomwe udatengedawa ndi atsamunda a ku Mangalande,owe adaukhzika ngati likulu lawo[[British Empire|British colonial administrative centre]]. Nthawi yomwe izi zidachitika koyambilila kwa dzaka za m'ma 1900. Chifuka chakuti mzindawu umapezeka pa njira yochoka ku mpoto ndi kulowela ku m'mwela kwa dziko la malawi,ndiposo pa mseu wopita ku [[Northen Rhodesia]] (tsopano [[Zambia]]),mzinda wa Lilongwe udakhala mzinda wawukulu zedi ku [[Malawi]]. Mu chaka cha 1974, Kapitolo ya dziko la Malawi idasunthidwa ku choka ku [[Zomba]] kupita ku boma la lilongwe. Ngakhale mzinda wa Lilongwe ndi kapitolo ya dziko la Malawi,ntchito za mbiri za chuma ndi malonda zi machitika mu mzinda wawukul mu dziko lonse la Malawi,[[Blantyre]] (the commercial capital of [[Malawi]]. Mu nthawi za posachedwa pompa, Paliyamenti idasamutsidwa kuchoka ku [[Zomba]] ndipo ndikukhazikitsidwa mu mzinda wa [[Lilongwe]]. Izi adapanga ndi mtogoleri yemwe akulamla dziko la [[Malawi]] panopo, [[Dr Bingu WaMuntharika]], ndipo mamembala a paliyamentiyi amayenera kukhala ku [[Lilongwe]],kwa nthawi yomwe paliyamenti ikukumana. Tsopano Lilongwe ndi pakati kati pa za ndale,pamene [[Blantyre]] ndi pakati kati pa za malonda.'''

